title: ArcheAge V1.2 Build 4.9 - HeadStart
description:
After reading some pages on the official forums from people having difficulties to download the game due to inability of loging into Glyph, I decided to put up this torrent that will help people preloading it.

You will need WinRar (http://rarlabs.com/download.htm) to unpack this file.

This archieve is 10.7GB and will unpack to a roughly 23GB folder containing all updated files up to v 1.2 Build 4.9 which is the HeadStart build.
